msgstr ""
"Ton code de vérification est : %1$s\n"
"\n"
"Il expire dans %2$d minutes. Si tu n'as pas essayé de te connecter, tu peux "
"ignorer cet e-mail."

#: includes/Auth/TwoFactorService.php:405
msgid ""
"Too many incorrect codes. Please enter your password again to restart "
