"Hi %1$s,\n"
"\n"
"Please verify your email address on %2$s by clicking the link below:\n"
"\n"
"%3$s\n"
"\n"
"This link expires in 48 hours.\n"
"\n"
"If you did not register, please ignore this email."
msgstr ""
"Salut %1$s,\n"
"\n"
"Vérifie ton adresse e-mail sur %2$s en cliquant sur le lien ci-dessous :\n"
"\n"
"%3$s\n"
"\n"
"Ce lien expire dans 48 heures.\n"
"\n"
"Si tu ne t'es pas inscrit, ignore cet e-mail."

#: includes/Auth/VerificationListener.php:294
#. translators: %s: site name
#, php-format
msgid "Confirm your new email address on %s"
msgstr "Confirme ta nouvelle adresse e-mail sur %s"

#: includes/Auth/VerificationListener.php:300
#. translators: 1: display name, 2: site name, 3: confirmation URL
#, php-format
msgid ""
"Hi %1$s,\n"
"\n"
"You asked to change the email address on your %2$s account to this inbox. "
